### Description

Currently, `@angular-devkit/build-angular:web-test-runner` [does not support](https://github.com/angular/angular-cli/blob/048df34ccb7d4ef67b5877e126c74c0db65b879c/packages/angular_devkit/build_angular/src/builders/web-test-runner/builder-status-warnings.ts#L24) creating code coverage reports - it would be great if this could be supported via the `codeCoverage` [option](https://angular.dev/guide/testing/code-coverage).

```json
"test": {
  "options": {
    "codeCoverage": true
  }
}
```

@web/test-runner supports a `--coverage` [flag](https://modern-web.dev/guides/test-runner/code-coverage/).



